    book_welcome_title: "ABAKETIWEYO",
    book_welcome_subtitle: "UMHLABA WONKE OZALWE EZIMPANDENI ZAKWA-KONGO...",
    book_welcome_desc: "Isolele ingumhlaba wombono ozalelwe ukubuyisela umphefumulo wokuxoxa izindaba zase-Afrika, umbuso wezinganekwane lapho amaqhawe akhethwa yisiphetho, izibusiso ezingakaze zikhohlakale, futhi amandla okhokho ephila kukho konke ikhasi, yonke isiprofetho, yonke impi. Yonke ingane efunda i-Isolele izothola amaqhawe abafana nayo, akhuluma ulimi lwayo, avikele izwe layo, futhi ahloniphe okhokho bayo. Lokhu kungenxa yesizukulwane esilandelayo samakhosi, izindlovukazi, amaqhawe, abasunguli, nabaxoxi bezindaba.",
    book_welcome_button: "HLOLA UMHLABA",
    
