    book_makanda_title: "MAKANDA",
    book_makanda_subtitle: "I-KANDAKE EKHUMAYO",
    book_makanda_desc: "Phakathi nendawo ye-Afrika Emaphakathi kwakukhona impucuko umhlaba owawungafanele yazi ngayo. Ivuswe ngokomoya. Ithuthuke kwezobuchwepheshe. Ivikelwe ngeLangabi Elingcwele. Lapho amandla angaphandle eza ukuthatha okwakungezabo, abakwaMakanda awazange awe. Banyamalala. Idolobho labo alizange lilahleke. Lalilinde lowo owazalelwa ukuphinda athwale ilangabi.",
