    book_bambula_subtitle: "ISAHLUKO I - ISIGUBHU EZINGCWELE",
    book_bambula_desc: "Ngaphambi kwamagama, kwakukhona isigyelo. UBambula wayeyingane eyayizwa konke. Lapho izigubhu zithathwa futhi izwe lithula, wagcina isigyelo siphila ngaphakathi kwakhe. Ehlome ngesigubhu esingcwele, uhamba phakathi kwezwe lemimoya nabaphilayo. Akalweli ukuze abhubhise. Uvikela ukuze akhumbule.",
    book_bambula_button: "THOLA U-BAMBULA",
    
