    book_mokele_desc: "UMokele akazalwa eyinkosi. Uzalelwe emshakalweni. Izitaladi zaseKinshasa zimfundisa ngaphambi kokuba isikole sikwazi, lapho ubuqotho butekenteke, udlame luyinto evamile, futhi ukusinda kuyikho konke. Kusukela enganeni kuye emgulukwini kuye enkosini. Wakha amandla, imali, nokuhlonishwa. EKinshasa, uyadliwa... Noma ube yisilwane esidla ezinye.",
    book_mokele_button: "THOLA U-MOKELE",
    
