    book_amara_desc: "Zonke izigebengu zasolwandle ziyalwesaba ulwandle. U-Amara ungumnikazi walo. UyiNdlovukazi Yolwandle. Ukaputeni owesatshwa kakhulu kuwo wonke amanzi emhlabeni. Asikho isikebhe esake sambalekela. Ayikho inkosi eyake yamhlakanipha. Ayikho ibutho lempi eyake yamisa imikhumbi yakhe. Kodwa u-Amara akahambi yedwa. Eceleni kwakhe kunezintokazi ezine eziboshwe ngigazi, ubuqotho nesiphetho. Izindlovukazi ezinhlanu zolwandle ezihlangene zithwala amandla azozamazamisa zonke izihlalo zobukhosi ezwekazini. Ngokuhlangana kwabo kuzalwa uhlozilwakwa-Agojie. Futhi kulolo hlozilwakwa kuvela izindlovukazi ezinhlanu eziyinkosi ezizoshintsha umzila womlando wase-Afrika unomphela. Lokhu akusiyona nje indaba yezigebengu zasolwandle. Lapha kulapho kuqala khona uhlozilwakazi olukhulu kunabo bonke emhlabeni we-ISOLELE.",
    book_amara_button: "THOLA U-AMARA",
    
    book_zattar_tag: "ZATTAR: INKOSANA YOMHLABA",
    book_zattar_title: "ZATTAR",
    book_zattar_subtitle: "UNQOBI WEZIHLOBO",
    book_zattar_desc: "Lapho Isiphetho Senqaba Yena Umbuso Owodwa, Wanquma Ukuwathatha Wonke. Inkosana uZattar wazalelwa ukuzuza isihlalo sobukhosi bakwaBapindi. Kodwa lapho Okhokho bekhetha omunye, okuthile ngaphakathi kwakhe akuzange kuphuke. Kwavutha. Wafunda iMpi Yokuqala neYesibili yaseVegas, izinganekwane zomonakalo ezazamazamisa umhlaba ngaphambi kokuba azalwe. Lapho abanye bebona isexwayiso, uZattar wabona imephu. Waqala iMpi Yesithathu yaseVegas. Hhayi ngobuhlanya. Hhayi ngenxa yobuhlungu. Kodwa ngenxa yokuthi wabuka umhlaba wonke wafinyelela esiphethweni esisodwa: Ungomunye umuntu. Futhi lowo muntu nguZattar. Akazange akhethwe. Ngakho-ke wakhetha umhlaba esikhundleni.",
    book_zattar_button: "THOLA U-ZATTAR",
    
